sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant API as ModelMesh API<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    participant Core as ModelMesh Core<br/>LRU Cache
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant OtherMM as Other ModelMesh Pod<br/>8080/TCP Litelinks<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>8085/TCP or UDS<br/>gRPC Plaintext

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 1: Inference Request Routing

    Client->>API: gRPC inference request<br/>mm-model-id: model-123<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    API->>Core: Route request (in-process)

    alt Model loaded locally
        Core->>Runtime: Forward inference request<br/>gRPC plaintext (localhost/UDS)
        Runtime-->>Core: Inference response
    else Model on another instance (cache miss)
        Core->>etcd: Lookup model location<br/>gRPC / TLS (optional)
        etcd-->>Core: Instance info
        Core->>OtherMM: Forward request via Litelinks<br/>gRPC/Thrift :8080 / TLS (optional)
        OtherMM->>Runtime: Forward to local runtime<br/>gRPC plaintext
        Runtime-->>OtherMM: Inference response
        OtherMM-->>Core: Response via Litelinks
    end

    Core-->>API: Response (in-process)
    API-->>Client: gRPC inference response

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Lifecycle (Register + Load)

    Client->>API: registerModel RPC<br/>gRPC :8033 / TLS + mTLS
    API->>Core: Register model (in-process)
    Core->>etcd: Store model record<br/>gRPC :2379 / TLS
    etcd-->>Core: Confirm registration
    Core->>Runtime: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC :8085 plaintext
    Runtime-->>Core: Model loaded (size info)
    Core->>etcd: Update model status → LOADED<br/>gRPC :2379 / TLS
    etcd-->>Core: Confirm update
    Core-->>API: Registration response
    API-->>Client: Model registered + loaded

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 3: VModel Transition (Zero-Downtime Update)

    Client->>API: setVModel RPC<br/>(vmodel-id → new-model-id)<br/>gRPC :8033 / TLS + mTLS
    API->>Core: VModel transition (in-process)
    Core->>etcd: Create/update vmodel record<br/>gRPC :2379 / TLS
    etcd-->>Core: Confirm vmodel record
    Core->>Runtime: loadModel (new target)<br/>gRPC :8085 plaintext
    Runtime-->>Core: New model loaded
    Core->>etcd: Promote target → active<br/>Atomic transition<br/>gRPC :2379 / TLS
    etcd-->>Core: Confirm promotion
    Core-->>API: VModel updated
    API-->>Client: VModel transition complete
